                                   .drag-n-drop__header__subtitle Please upload a file type with these extensions: pdf

                              .drag-n-drop__error-file-size
                                   .drag-n-drop__header__image
                                        +icon-error-file-size()
                                   .drag-n-drop__header__title Whoops, file is to large ðŸ¤­
                                   .drag-n-drop__header__subtitle Maximum upload file is 20MB

                              .drag-n-drop__error-connection-lost
                                   .drag-n-drop__header__image
                                        +icon-error-connection-lost()
                                   .drag-n-drop__header__title Whoops, Internet connection lost ðŸ˜¢
                                   .drag-n-drop__header__subtitle
                                        | There seems to be problem with your internet connections,
                                        | please check your settings or switch offline mode

                         .button-file-wrapper.wow.fadeInDown(data-wow-duration=".5s" data-wow-delay=".8s")
                              +button().button--file
                                   label.button--file__label
                                        | Choose a PDF
                                        input.button--file__label__input-file(type="file" accept="application/pdf")

